      <title>特朗普的3美元汽油梦仍然对美国驾驶员而言遥不可及</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-s-3-gasoline-dream-is-still-far-off-for-american-drivers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统吹捧了美国人在关税推出期间为汽油支付不到3美元的想法。即使原油市场趋势低落，燃料的成本仍然固执地高于该水平，并且看起来将保持这种状态。至少现在。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-s-3-gasoline-dream-is-still-far-off-for-american-drivers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 18:22:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
